Ward {2}
At the beginning of your end step, if a nontoken creature died this turn, create a 1/1 black Skeleton creature token.
Sacrifice another creature: Target creature you control gains lifelink and deathtouch until end of turn.

Equipped creature gets +2/+1.
When equipped creature dies, if it wasn't a token, create a 1/1 black Skeleton creature token, then attach Onyx-Crest Sword to that token.
